Q_NAME: Finding of Biggest of Two Numbers
Q_DESC:
Mandatory
1.Create a new class named Biggest apart from the main class(TestClass)
2.Create two methods read() and biggest() to read two integers and to find the biggest of two numbers respectively with no arguments and of type void.
3.Create an object bs for the Biggest class in the main class and access read() and biggest() methods created inside Biggest class.
